{"kind":"article","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The ultimate challenge is to compete against a skilled opponent, and Game Center makes it easy for your players to discover each other and play together over a network. Understand the process to add players to a multi-player match. Go into the details of peer-to-peer and server-hosted multiplayer games. Learn about sending data or game state to remote players, and discuss how you can take advantage of in-game voice chat."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC11","title":"Multi-Player Gaming with Game Center"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-410-MultiPlayer-Gaming-with-Game-Center","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-410-multiplayer-gaming-with-game-center"]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/410\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"WWDC11.jpeg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC11.jpeg"}